instruct_text:
In this task you will judge whether a string of letters forms a word or not (i.e., is a nonword). Look at the cross at the start of each trial. After a second, a string of letters will appear. Your task is to indicate if the letter string forms a word or not (i.e., if it is a nonword).

 For example, AUTHOR is a word while AUTHON is a nonword.

Press the space bar or click the button below to continue.
